{"id":29490055983,"name":"Test","node_id":"WFR_kwLOA_1uaM8AAAAG3b6LLw","head_branch":"fix/dvs-lastupdated-params_2.43","head_sha":"6dfd45684a36003aede908a83574ebefe8d25edb","path":".github/workflows/run-tests.yml","run_number":54768,"run_attempt":1,"event":"pull_request","display_title":"backport: fix: lastUpdated/lastUpdatedDuration alone incorrectly rejected on dataValueSets export [DHIS2-21821]","status":"completed","conclusion":"success","workflow_id":10954,"check_suite_id":79842391015,"check_suite_node_id":"CS_kwDOA_1uaM8AAAASlvoz5w","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29490055983","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29490055983","created_at":"2026-07-16T10:13:29Z","updated_at":"2026-07-16T10:29:55Z","run_started_at":"2026-07-16T10:13:29Z","jobs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29490055983/jobs","logs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29490055983/logs","check_suite_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/check-suites/79842391015","artifacts_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29490055983/artifacts","cancel_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29490055983/cancel","rerun_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29490055983/rerun","head_commit":{"message":"fix: lastUpdated/lastUpdatedDuration alone incorrectly rejected on dataValueSets export [DHIS2-21821] (#24465)\n\n* fix: lastUpdated/lastUpdatedDuration alone incorrectly rejected on dataValueSets export [DHIS2-21821]\n\nDataExportParams.hasPeriodFilters() dropped the lastUpdated/lastUpdatedDuration\nchecks during the 2.43 SQL-based export rewrite (#22406), so GET /dataValueSets\nrequests using only lastUpdatedDuration (no period/date range) were rejected\nwith E2002, even though the parameter is documented and still wired into the\nunderlying query. Restores the pre-2.43 validation behavior.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 5 \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e\n\n* fix: separate lastUpdated validation from period-filter query building [DHIS2-21821]\n\nThe previous fix broadened DataExportParams.hasPeriodFilters() to also\naccept lastUpdated/lastUpdatedDuration, but that method is also used by\nHibernateDataExportStore to decide whether to build the pe_ids CTE/JOIN\nfor actual period-table filtering. Broadening it caused a spurious\npe_ids join to appear whenever only lastUpdated/lastUpdatedDuration was\nset, breaking DataExportQueryBuilderTest#testFilter_LastUpdated.\n\nIntroduces a separate hasLastUpdatedFilters() predicate and combines it\nwith hasPeriodFilters() only at the E2002 validation call site in\nDefaultDataExportService, leaving hasPeriodFilters() semantics (and the\nquery builder behavior that depends on them) unchanged.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 5 \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e\n\n* test: verify SQL actually applies lastUpdated/lastUpdatedDuration as a real filter [DHIS2-21821]\n\nThe existing testFilter_LastUpdated only asserted that a parameter named\n\"lastUpdated\" was used, not its bound value, and there was no coverage\nat all for lastUpdatedDuration. This left the duration-to-date\nconversion in HibernateDataExportStore untested: a regression there\n(e.g. dropping the conversion) would silently erase the WHERE clause\nvia eraseNullParameterLines(), turning the filter into a no-op without\nany test catching it.\n\nAdds paramValue() to AbstractQueryBuilderTest to expose bound parameter\nvalues for assertions beyond exact-match SQL/param-name checks. Adds\ntestFilter_LastUpdatedDuration and strengthens testFilter_LastUpdated\nto assert the actual bound date. Verified by temporarily reverting the\nduration-to-date conversion in HibernateDataExportStore and confirming\ntestFilter_LastUpdatedDuration fails with the exact \"WHERE 1=1\" no-op\nsymptom, then restoring it.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 5 \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e\n\n---------\n\nCo-authored-by: Claude Sonnet 5 \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e","author":{"name":"Jason Pickering","email":"jason@dhis2.org"},"id":"6dfd45684a36003aede908a83574ebefe8d25edb","tree_id":"8ce6ddd630ce0af88fc17bcf94a6bfd4a9b10550","timestamp":"2026-07-16T10:13:20Z","committer":{"name":"Jason Pickering","email":"jason@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/subscriptions"},"name":"dhis2-core","full_name":"dhis2/dhis2-core","description":"DHIS 2 Core. Written in Java. Contains the service layer and Web API.","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core","fork":false,"private":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core","archive_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/{archive_format}{/ref}","assignees_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/assignees{/user}","blobs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/git/blobs{/sha}","branches_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/branches{/branch}","collab